OL,3,CHospital's Chief Nurse apologises to
OL,4,Cfamilies unhappy with their maternity
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FAllegations labelled at the hospital,
OL,8,Fwhich date as far back as 2007,
OL,9,Finclude substandard care, preventable
OL,10,Fdeaths, traumatic birthing
OL,11,Fexperiences, denied caesarians and
OL,12,FPTSD.
OL,14,F"I am deeply sorry to all of the women
OL,15,Fand families who feel that we have let
OL,16,Fthem down, particularly at a time when
OL,17,Fwe needed them," said Yvonne Christley.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
