OL,3,CHospital's Chief Nurse apologises to
OL,4,Cfamilies unhappy with their maternity
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,F"Our safety and our maternity and
OL,8,Fneonatal outcomes, are really good. We
OL,9,Fdo know that as a service, we have
OL,10,Fareas that we wish to focus on and
OL,11,Fimprove. And in particular, that is
OL,12,Faround patient experience.
OL,14,F"We've invested heavily, more than
OL,15,Fthree million pounds over the last two
OL,16,Fyears on increasing our midwifery
OL,17,Fstaffing, on enhancing our leadership
OL,18,Fand improving the facilities that our
OL,19,Fwomen and families use."
