OL,7,FWhen challenged about meeting these
OL,8,Ffamilies face-to-face, Yvonne
OL,9,FChristley said they will be meeting
OL,10,Fwith them in September: "We are really
OL,11,Fkeen to work with these families, to
OL,12,Funderstand their experiences and to
OL,13,Fensure that we work together to
OL,14,Fimprove our service."
OL,16,FShe denied there was a toxic culture
OL,17,Fin the maternity department following
OL,18,Fclaims some staff are rude and don't
OL,19,Flisten to patients.
