OL,7,FOxford is not currently part of that
OL,8,Flist, and campaigners are keen to see
OL,9,Fthe hospital included in any future
OL,10,Finvestigations lead by the Government.
OL,12,FWhen asked if Yvonne Christley would
OL,13,Fwork with Mr Streeting on an
OL,14,Finvestigation, she twice refused to
OL,15,Fconfirm whether she would comply:
OL,16,F"maternity services are always subject
OL,17,Fto external scrutiny. And we welcome
OL,18,Fany opportunity to listen, to learn
OL,19,Fand to improve our services."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
