OL,7,FWhen pressed again, she said: "as an
OL,8,Forganisation and as a maternity
OL,9,Fservice we are subject to quite
OL,10,Fconsiderable external review and
OL,11,Fscrutiny.
OL,13,F"We are a learning organisation. We're
OL,14,Falways willing to embrace improvements
OL,15,Fand would welcome any opportunity to
OL,16,Fdemonstrate the safety and quality of
OL,17,Four services."
