OL,3,CHospital's Chief Nurse apologises to
OL,4,Cfamilies unhappy with their maternity
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FAs a world-leading research hospital,
OL,8,Fshe said that despite any damage to
OL,9,Ftheir reputation, they "expect to
OL,10,Fcontinue regardless of what's
OL,11,Fhappening externally.
OL,13,F"We deliver 7,500 births every year.
OL,14,FAnd, for the most part, we have
OL,15,Ftremendously positive feedback. I want
OL,16,Fto get that right for every single
OL,17,Fwomen and every single family."
