OL,3,CHospital's Chief Nurse apologises to
OL,4,Cfamilies unhappy with their maternity
OL,5,Ccare
OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesperson said: "We inherited an
OL,9,Funacceptable situation where too many
OL,10,Ffamilies, including those in
OL,11,FOxfordshire, suffered trauma, harm and
OL,12,Floss due to failures in maternity care.
OL,14,F"We are committed to breaking that
OL,15,Fcycle and providing mothers and babies
OL,16,Fwith the safe, compassionate care they
OL,17,Fdeserve. That is why we have announced
OL,18,Fa rapid national investigation, led by
OL,19,FBaroness Amos, to identify where
OL,20,Fthings are going wrong and fix it.
